OL,3,CScammers use profile of ITV journalist
OL,4,Cwho died from cancer
OL,6,FFraudsters are using the profiles of
OL,7,Fprominent and respected public figures
OL,8,Fto promote an online cryptocurrency
OL,9,Fscam.
OL,11,FThey include ITV News journalist Gary
OL,12,FBurgess, one of the most recognisable
OL,13,Ffigures in the Channel Islands, who
OL,14,Fdied from terminal cancer in 2022.
OL,16,FThe fake positive reviews include real
OL,17,Fphotos and made up quotes to encourage
OL,18,Fpeople to invest money, promising
OL,19,Flarge returns.
