OL,3,CScammers use profile of ITV journalist
OL,4,Cwho died from cancer
OL,6,FThe ad falsely claims Gary made more
OL,7,Fthan #8,700 using a crypto trading
OL,8,Fplatform, quoting him as saying: "I've
OL,9,Fonly used it for a couple of weeks and
OL,10,FI've already made more money from it
OL,11,Fthan I do busting my butt off at work
OL,12,Ffor months!"
OL,14,FCryptocurrency is a digital form of
OL,15,Fmoney that allows people to pay each
OL,16,Fother online and is largely
OL,17,Funregulated.
OL,19,FITV News showed Gary's widower Alan
OL,20,FBurgess the fake review.
