OL,7,Fviolating, I'm just angry.
OL,9,F"The fact that someone would do this,
OL,10,Fknowing or not the fact that Gary has
OL,11,Fdied, to use the image in this way and
OL,12,Ftake advantage of the goodwill Gary
OL,13,Fhad from the people of Jersey is
OL,14,Finfuriating."
OL,16,FA review falsely claiming to represent
OL,17,Fthe head of Jersey's Judiciary,
OL,18,FBailiff Sir Timothy Le Cocq, is also
OL,19,Fbeing promoted by the same fraudsters
OL,20,F- saying he made around #4,600.
